Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: bump
Version: 0.3.0
Summary: Bumps package version numbers
Home-page: https://github.com/marksteve/bump
Author: Mark Steve Samson
Author-email: hello@marksteve.com
License: MIT
Description: bump
        ====
        
        Bumps package versions
        
        Usage:
        ------
        
        Bump patch version ::
        
            $ bump setup.py
            1.0.2 => 1.0.3
            Is this ok? y/n y
            Updated setup.py
        
        Bump minor version ::
        
            $ bump setup.py -m
            1.0.3 => 1.1.0
            Is this ok? y/n y
            Updated setup.py
        
        Bump major version ::
        
            $ bump setup.py -M
            1.1.0 => 2.0.0
            Is this ok? y/n y
            Updated setup.py
        
        Add suffix ::
            
            $ bump setup.py -M -s=-rc
            2.0.0 => 3.0.0-rc
            Is this ok? y/n y
            Updated setup.py
        
        Quiet mode ::
        
            $ bump setup.py -q
            3.0.1-rc
        
Keywords: bump increment package version
Platform: UNKNOWN
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 2.7
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 3
Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 3.1
